N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 606.11 - Regular meetings

State Regulations

Regular meetings of the council shall be held twice a year
at such times and places as may be designated by the president. All meetings
shall be conducted under Robert's Rules of Order. Notes
